Collecting Summon Materials

The materials needed to raise your summons' levels can be obtained from World of Illusions quests.
*Materials and quests will differ depending on the summon's level.
Summon LV Where to Find Materials
21～30 "World of Illusions Ultimate" quest rewards, etc.
31～40 Unlocking illusion board spaces with points obtained from World of Illusions Divine, etc.
41～50 Completing Spiritus missions in World of Illusions Spiritus
